    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Non-technical skills (People skill/soft skills):&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Ability to mentor and coach&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Leadership&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Communication&amp;nbsp;and collaboration&lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></skills>
